title: 이달의소녀탐구 #475 (LOONA TV #475)
summary:
It's their last shooting day in Paris.
0:08 -- Go Won knows that Hyejoo has a scene with a choker. She points out that the bruise on her neck makes it look like she is hurt.
0:22 -- Go Won: "She has to do it with grace" (as she acts out her taking of the choker)
0:30 -- She isn't sure if Hyejoo can do it nicely.
0:36 -- She does it with style.
The filming is over and they sign off by talking about how they enjoyed the week.
